snippet.title: Path of Exile 2 - Official Aggorat Teaser Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description: Grinding Gear Games debuted a new trailer for Path of Exile 2, as the hero hacks, slashes, and electrocutes every monster that stands in their way. More information about the sequel to the hit action RPG game will be revealed during an event on July 28.
